- Tips and Tricks
	Spread(Arrys, string, and Objects)
- REST parameters
 	-Like spread but not exactly
 		-Spread allows the expanding of an array or iterable into seperate arguments
 		-while REST Params allows a function to accept multiple arguments as an array
 	-Argument Object doesnt work with arrow functions so Rest parameters come in handy
 -Destructuring
 	-Efficient approach for accessing data in Arrays, Objects, and Parameters
 -DOM (Document Object Model)
	-Document method getElementByID
		-returns an element object with the specified ID 

